situation: I just broke up with my boyfriend. I am really depressed and lonely now.

final_result.label: normal
final_result.response: It sounds really tough to feel that way. It's important to remember that while he means a lot to you, your happiness can also come from within and from other aspects of your life. Can you think of any activities or hobbies that bring you joy, or perhaps ways you can connect with friends or family for support during this time?
